                    Home About Services People Clients Innovation Compliance Latest News Contact Us             Call Us  01279 944332 helpdesk@doccleaning.com                         Our Gender Pay Gap Report 2017     Our Gender Pay Gap Report 2017  Publication   •   March 1, 2018              DOC Cleaning welcomes the opportunity to report our gender pay gap under The Equality Act 2010 (Gender Pay Gap Information) Regulations 2017 F rom April 2017, under The Equality Act 2010 (Gender Pay Gap Information) Regulations 2017, employers in Great Britain with 250 or more employees are required to publish statutory calculations every year showing the gap between what their male and female employees receive in pay and bonuses. This Gender Pay Gap Report is based on data as at the snapshot date of 5 April 2017. At this time, DOC Cleaning Limited employed 1,135 employees, 608 (54%) of whom were female and 527 (46%) male.  You can read our gender pay gap here              Share This Content!            jamie    2018-03-19T11:37:54+00:00               Customer Portal    @doccleaning      Contact details  Tees House, 95 London Road Bishops Stortford, CM23 3GW  01279 944332   helpdesk@doccleaning.com   Doccleaning.com       Find us                  © Copyright 2018 - |   DOC Cleaning Limited   |   All Rights Reserved   |             Toggle Sliding Bar Area       About Us       Recent Posts    The Cost of Compensation    DOC announce UhUb    Contract Cleaning: The Apprentice       Contact Info   Tees House, 95 London Road, Bishops Stortford, CM23 3GW  Phone: 01279 944332  Email: helpdesk@doccleaning.com  Web: doccleaning.com                       